            exts: {}
            customProperties: {}
            customText: >-
              This room is created dynamically with perlin noise.

              For the sake of simplicity of the template,

              only the area around the character is made empty,

              thus the level can turn out to be unwalkable.


              Click the "Procedural" button again to re-roll the level.


              There are many approaches to level generation,

              thus a proper level generation algorithm is not  implemented here
              —

              search for existing one among the internet or invent your own!
            customSize: !<tag:yaml.org,2002:js/undefined> ''
            customWordWrap: !<tag:yaml.org,2002:js/undefined> ''
            bindings: {}
